^ Kellock, Andrew (20 October 2016). "Woman who invented disposable nappies has died, aged 94, at her Highland home". The Press and Journal. Retrieved 20 October 2016. 
^ a b Lawson, Jim (19 October 2016). "Scottish inventor of the disposable nappy dies at 94". www.scotsman.com. The Scotsman. Retrieved 20 October 2016. 
^ a b c "Paddi Pads Fleecy Disposable Soft Napkins | Mrs Valerie Hunter-Gordon | V&A Search the Collections". collections.vam.ac.uk. V&A Museum. Retrieved 20 October 2016. 
