Raspberry London


 








Ione Hunter Gordon
Ione studied and worked in Florence, Italy from 2010 to 2015. There she studied and taught traditional time honoured methods of painting and drawing and material preparation. Favouring oil paint, charcoal and pencil Ione spends her time creating portraits and figurative work. She has exhibited in group shows across the United States of America, Europe, and within the UK. She now resides in the UK dividing her time between commissions, private work, and teaching.



